{"TopicId":165291,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"Antenna / Battery Status","CreatedByName":"cyberKerb","CreatedById":28891,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T04:55:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cyberKerb","CreatedById":28891,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T04:55:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nResearching the KSP API, I found that the status property of an Antenna is not settable, which is a bugger when I want the ability to set it to be broken for a mod idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there any other ways to set an antenna to the stock status of \u0022broken\u0022? Or is the only option to write a new \u003Cspan\u003EModule (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/DangIt/blob/master/source/DangIt/Failure%20modules/DeployableAntenna.cs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Elike DangIt\u003C/a\u003E) \u003C/span\u003Efor all antennas that allow it to be broken \u0022on purpose\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the battery values - is there a way to set an unloaded ship entire EC value to 0? Ie I\u0027m wanting the vessel to have zero EC upon in loading into physics range / becoming active vessel? Or would resource catch-up mechanics likely override the 0 value I set at an\u00A0prior point in time went unloaded?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-09-08T05:15:11Z\u0022 title=\u002209/08/2017 05:15  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 8, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by wile1411\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T09:25:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nModuleDeployableAntenna extends \u003Ca href=\u0022http://docuwiki-kspapi.rhcloud.com/#/classes/ModuleDeployablePart\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EModuleDeployablePart\u003C/a\u003E. You have a\u00A0breakPanels() method in there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cyberKerb","CreatedById":28891,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T10:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome and thanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57146-sarbian/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257146\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57146-sarbian/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@sarbian\u003C/a\u003E - running testing now. Any thought on zeroing the EC?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-09-08T10:43:27Z\u0022 title=\u002209/08/2017 10:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 8, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by wile1411\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-08T11:26:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223167875\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165291\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221504867388\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002228891\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wile1411\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, wile1411 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome and thanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57146-sarbian/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257146\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?